"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?27/57/28562?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Nausea and vomiting in adults (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?9/5/9299?source=see_link\">",
