"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?34/51/35634?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: High-fiber diet (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?36/16/37121?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: What are clinical trials? (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?35/29/36308?source=see_link\">",
