"    </div>",
"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"     Reproduced with permission from: Scarfone RJ, Cho CS. Cardioversion and Defibrillation. In: Textbook of Pediatric Emergency Procedures, 2nd ed, King C, Henretig FM (Eds), Lippincott Williams &amp; Wilkins, Philadelphia 2008. Copyright &copy; 2008 Lippincott Williams &amp; Wilkins.",
"    </div>",
